## Three parts 
1. Language specific
2. Culture specific (Choose a culture and get information accordingly)
3. Region specific (Choose a region and explore all its cultures)

## Culture Specific
1. Literatures
2. Arts
3. History
4. Festivals
5. Lifestyle
6. Important places
7. Rituals
8. All-over summary

## Region Specific
1. List of all the cultures in that region
2. All-over summary
3. History